#### B. Component Styles
All components must use:
- Tailwind utility classes
- Dark mode variants (`dark:`)
- RTL variants (`rtl:`) for Arabic/Farsi
- Focus-visible styles
- Hover/active states

#### C. Accessibility
- WCAG 2.2 AA compliance
- Contrast ratios ≥4.5:1 (text), ≥3:1 (UI)
- Keyboard navigation
- Screen reader support
- Focus indicators

